The paper deals with answering queries on data, which is a common topic in database systems (cs.DB). The use of access methods and constraints also suggests relevance to information retrieval (cs.IR) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of decision procedures and complexity analysis, which are common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cryptography (cs.CR).
